transcript.text: Hello, in this video we will learn about what is category and category groups and how to create them.
Let's talk about the benefits.
Categories help in organizing products in a way that makes it easy for visitors to find out what they're looking for.
It helps to manage your products by assigning them into a category and group.
It reduces the long list of products displayed on the homepage.
Have a look at the storefront.
When we click on category group, commercial printing, you can see all the categories showing as a drop down and further we can see all the products list showing.
Similarly, all the category groups you can show on the navigation bar which arrange category groups, categories and products.
Let's have a look at the admin, We have to go to products, product categories and then we can see two tabs.
One is product category and another is category group.
In the product category section you will see a list of all the categories with images.
For enabling category group you have to go to Store configuration, site settings.
Search category and enable Product category.
Product category with group.
Select Yes with group.
To add a new product category, click on Add Product category, Fill category title.
Select Category group.
From the drop down list, Add Category Image Status set to active and save it.
Similarly, to Add category group, click on Add Category group, fill in the details Category Title, Category Image status set to active and save.
Thanks for watching this video.
Feel free to connect with us in case of any concern.
